" align cursor on new line with old line
set autoindent
" case-insensitive search
set ignorecase
" print helpful messages (eg, '4 lines yanked')
set report=1
" show matching parens, braces, etc
set showmatch
" display current mode (insert/normal)
set showmode

" This config is used to customize vi.
" See 'man ex' for all available settings.
" Run ':set all' to show current settings.

" This comment is at the bottom of the file because 'vi' doesn't seem
" to load the settings when it is at the top.
